\par 
\par }{\b\f1 Confirm Entry Deletion
\par }{\f1 
\par If you select this option, Add/Remove Plus! will prompt for confirmation before deleting a program from the Add/Remove Programs list.
\par 
\par }{\b\f1 Confirm Application Uninstall
\par }{\f1 
\par If you select this option, Add/Remove Plus! will prompt for confirmation before uninstalling a program.
\par 
\par }{\b\f1 Ensure removal from the Add/Remove list
\par }{\f1 
\par If you select this option, Add/Remove Plus! will ensure that the program is also removed from the Add/Remove Programs list after it is removed from your computer.
\par 
\par }{\b\f1 Show a question mark near missing uninstallers}{\f1 
\par 
\par If you select this option, Add/Remove Plus! will show a question mark near the applications that are missing their uninstall program. This helps you to quickly find which applications have been removed from your computer, but not from the Add/Remove list.

